methods.getSafepointCount:
Returns the number of safepoints taken place since the Java virtual machine started.

:return: (long) the number of safepoints taken place since the Java virtual machine started.
methods.getSafepointSyncTimeMillis:
Returns the accumulated time spent getting to safepoints in milliseconds.

:return: (long) the accumulated time spent getting to safepoints in milliseconds.
methods.getTotalSafepointTimeMillis:
Returns the accumulated time spent at safepoints in milliseconds. This is the accumulated elapsed time that the
 application has been stopped for safepoint operations.

:return: (long) the accumulated time spent at safepoints in milliseconds.
